    <entry>
      <title>近两月的学习成果</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/06/jin-liang-yue-de-xue-xi-cheng-guo/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/06/jin-liang-yue-de-xue-xi-cheng-guo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>因为<strong>疫情</strong>的原因,导致在家呆了两个月,也学习了两个月,在<strong>tomcat</strong> 的<strong>webapps</strong>目录下塞满了<strong>war包</strong></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/imag/20200306094854.png" alt=""></p><p>以下来介绍一下我的<strong>学习成果</strong></p><h2 id="Perfume商店"><a href="#Perfume商店" class="headerlink" title="Perfume商店"></a>Perfume商店</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/imag/20200306095312.png" alt=""></p><p><strong>香水商店</strong>,经过一次一次的升级,有三个版本,是技术推进的结果.</p><p>三个版本概述:</p><ol><li><strong>perfume</strong>是直接在<strong>jsp</strong>之中循环展示商品;</li><li><strong>perfume-2</strong>是新增了购物车的功能,这里学习到了<strong>ajax</strong> 局部刷新技术;</li><li><strong>perfume-3</strong>使用<strong>JSTL</strong>来简化繁琐的循环和数据的获取</li></ol><p>链接:</p><ol><li><a href="http://47.115.33.215/perfume/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/perfume/</a></li><li><a href="http://47.115.33.215/perfume-2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/perfume-2/</a></li><li><a href="http://47.115.33.215/perfume-3/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/perfume-3/</a></li></ol><h2 id="主页"><a href="#主页" class="headerlink" title="主页"></a>主页</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/imag/20200306100019.png" alt=""></p><p>这个主页原本的打算是用来当<strong>个人博客</strong>用的,在后期写博客的时候发现了局限性,以至于博客迁移在这里.</p><p>链接: <a href="http://47.115.33.215/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/</a></p><h2 id="武汉加油项目"><a href="#武汉加油项目" class="headerlink" title="武汉加油项目"></a>武汉加油项目</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/imag/20200306100448.png" alt=""></p><p>在疫情的之下,让我们为武汉人民加油,<strong>武汉加油,中国加油!</strong></p><p>链接: <a href="http://47.115.33.215/fighting-wuhan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/fighting-wuhan/</a></p><h2 id="水果商店"><a href="#水果商店" class="headerlink" title="水果商店"></a>水果商店</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/imag/20200306161742.png" alt=""></p><p>总体来说跟<strong>perfume</strong>商店是差不多的,使用到了<strong>Modal</strong>跟<strong>Dao</strong>层,渐渐有<strong>MVC</strong>的味道了.</p><p>链接: <a href="http://47.115.33.215/fruitProj2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/fruitProj2/</a></p><h2 id="生活商城"><a href="#生活商城" class="headerlink" title="生活商城"></a>生活商城</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/imag/20200306161905.png" alt=""></p><p>这是最近这次<strong>实验报告</strong>的商城,有<strong>登录</strong>功能等,主要是用来理解<strong>request</strong>和<strong>response</strong>的功能和奥义.</p><p>链接: <a href="http://47.115.33.215/market/index.jsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://47.115.33.215/market/index.jsp</a></p><h2 id="PicGo-Github-实现图床"><a href="#PicGo-Github-实现图床" class="headerlink" title="PicGo + Github 实现图床"></a>PicGo + Github 实现图床</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/img/20200306162516.png" alt=""></p><p><strong>微博图床</strong>无法使用之后,写博客的一片哀嚎.</p><p>使用<strong>PicGO + Github</strong> 就是一套解决方案,中间采用了<strong>GitHub</strong>的<strong>CDN</strong>加速,避免了访问速度慢的缺点.</p><h2 id="学习Linux"><a href="#学习Linux" class="headerlink" title="学习Linux"></a>学习Linux</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlezachary/images/img/20200306162553.png" alt=""></p><p>自从领了新的云服务器,就去搞了去<strong>Ubuntu</strong>系统,在<strong>cmd</strong>式的交互下,安装<strong>tomcat</strong>,<strong>mysql</strong>等一些东西,还是有点快乐的.</p><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>以上便是这两个月的总结，学的不多，继续努力！<strong>fighting！</strong></p><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 总结 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
